<h1 id="introduction">Introduction</h1>

<p><a href="https://github.com/nvbn/thefuck">TheFuck</a> command/program is a command that corrects commands that you typed incorrectly, for example: Assuming you wrote <code class="highlighter-rouge">aptget install vim</code>, and then you type fuck, it automatically corrects your command by typing it correctly, according to the examples shown in the gif below :</p>

<!-- LISTA MIN -->
<script async="" src="//pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js"></script>

