<h2 id="how-to-install-this">How to INSTALL this?</h2>

<p>Try searching with your distro‚Äôs package manager, for example in Gentoo I searched and there is in <a href="https://wiki.gentoo.org/wiki/Portage">Portage</a>, then to install just run:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"><span class="nb">sudo </span>emerge thefuck</code></pre></figure>

<p>Use your distro‚Äôs search tool!</p>

<p><img src="/assets/img/commands/emerge-search-thefuck.png" alt="Seach distro" /></p>

<p>But if not, install via <a href="https://github.com/nvbn/thefuck">TheFuck‚Äôs GitHub</a>.</p>

