<h2 id="running-the-fuck">Running the fuck!</h2>

<p>Well, to use you have already seen that it is very simple, but if you have any questions or want to check options and/or customizations, use the help of the program for more information: <code class="highlighter-rouge">fuck --help</code>.</p>

<p>In my case I tried to open a file with Nano, but then a message was generated and I used fuck and he corrected it automatically! üòú</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">nano file.txt
Noob text editor detected. Command cannot be executed
fuck
vim file.txt</code></pre></figure>

